RSI Platform Rack

The complete roof rack system.

1560Lx1345Wx90H

Perfect for:

  • Roof Top Tents
  • Surf Boards / Kayaks
  • Awnings / Jerry Can Holders
  • Equipment & building supplies

 

Click here to view the entire range of RSI Canopies/Assesories available!

Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!

 

Please note: Depending on stock & availability, the current wait time for this product is approx. 30 – 90 days from date of order.
